---
import Layout from '../../components/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Company — Mentyx.ai"
  description="Learn about Mentyx.ai - The intelligence behind every loan. Transforming lending with AI-powered automation."
  canonical="https://mentyx.ai/about/company"
>

<main class="company-main">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="hero-badge">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/>
            <path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/>
            <path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
          </svg>
          <span>About Mentyx.ai</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="hero-title">
          The Intelligence Behind <span class="title-gradient">Every Loan</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">
          We're building the future of lending infrastructure — where every decision is faster, smarter, and more accurate.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission Section -->
  <section class="mission-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="mission-grid">
        <div class="mission-text">
          <h2 class="section-title">Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="text-large">
            To empower lenders with <span class="ai-text">AI</span>-powered tools that eliminate manual processes, reduce risk, and unlock growth — without sacrificing control or compliance.
          </p>
          <p class="text-muted">
            We believe lending should be instant, transparent, and intelligent. Every loan officer deserves technology that works as hard as they do.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="stats-card">
          <div class="stat-item">
            <div class="stat-value">50+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Lenders using Mentyx</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-divider"></div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <div class="stat-value">$2B+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Loans processed</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-divider"></div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <div class="stat-value">60%</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Faster underwriting</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story Section -->
  <section class="story-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">Our Story</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          From idea to innovation — six years of transforming lending
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3 class="timeline-title">2019 - The Spark</h3>
            <p class="timeline-text">
              The idea for Mentyx was born. Our founders spent years in private lending and witnessed the same frustration everywhere: talented underwriters drowning in manual work, lenders losing deals to faster competitors, and borrowers waiting weeks for answers.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3 class="timeline-title">2020-2021 - Deep Research</h3>
            <p class="timeline-text">
              We interviewed 100+ lenders, underwriters, and borrowers to understand the real problems. The message was clear: they didn't need another generic LOS — they needed intelligent automation built specifically for asset-based lending.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3 class="timeline-title">2022 - Foundation Built</h3>
            <p class="timeline-text">
              Development began on the core platform. We assembled a team of engineers who understood both lending and <span class="ai-text">AI</span>, building the foundation for intelligent document processing and automated underwriting.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3 class="timeline-title">2023 - First Lenders</h3>
            <p class="timeline-text">
              Mentyx.ai launched with our first pilot customers. Early adopters processed their first automated loans, cutting underwriting time from days to hours. The platform proved that speed and accuracy weren't mutually exclusive.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3 class="timeline-title">2024 - Rapid Growth</h3>
            <p class="timeline-text">
              We crossed $500M in loans processed and expanded to 25+ active lenders. Our <span class="ai-text">AI</span> underwriting engine achieved 95%+ accuracy, and we launched real-time portfolio monitoring for multi-affiliate lending groups.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3 class="timeline-title">2025 - Scale & Innovation</h3>
            <p class="timeline-text">
              Today, we're powering 50+ lenders across the United States, processing over $2B in annual loan volume. Our platform handles everything from application to oversight, and we're continuously innovating with explainable <span class="ai-text">AI</span> and predictive analytics.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3 class="timeline-title">The Future - Market Leadership</h3>
            <p class="timeline-text">
              We're just getting started. Our vision: to become the intelligence layer for every private real estate lender in the United States — making asset-based lending faster, smarter, and more accessible.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values Section -->
  <section class="values-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">Our Values</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">The principles that guide everything we do</p>
      </div>

      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="value-title">Speed with Precision</h3>
          <p class="value-text">
            We believe you shouldn't have to choose between fast and accurate. Our <span class="ai-text">AI</span> delivers both.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="value-title">Security First</h3>
          <p class="value-text">
            Your data is your most valuable asset. We treat it that way with bank-grade encryption and compliance.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="value-title">Customer Obsessed</h3>
          <p class="value-text">
            We succeed when you succeed. Your feedback shapes every feature we build.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Backed By Section -->
  <section class="backed-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="backed-content">
        <div class="backed-text">
          <h2 class="section-title">Backed by Industry Leaders</h2>
          <p class="text-large">
            Our investors and advisors include former executives from major financial institutions and successful fintech companies.
          </p>
          <p class="text-muted">
            We're supported by people who understand lending from the inside and believe in our vision for a smarter, faster future.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="backed-stats-grid">
          <div class="backed-stat-card">
            <div class="backed-stat-value">100+</div>
            <div class="backed-stat-label">Years combined lending experience</div>
          </div>
          <div class="backed-stat-card">
            <div class="backed-stat-value">$5B+</div>
            <div class="backed-stat-label">Portfolio managed by advisors</div>
          </div>
          <div class="backed-stat-card">
            <div class="backed-stat-value">25+</div>
            <div class="backed-stat-label">Active lending partners</div>
          </div>
          <div class="backed-stat-card">
            <div class="backed-stat-value">15+</div>
            <div class="backed-stat-label">States with lenders</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2 class="cta-title">Join us in transforming lending</h2>
        <p class="cta-subtitle">See how Mentyx can help your lending operation</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="https://calendly.com/contact-mentyx/30min" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
            Schedule Demo
            <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="/about/careers" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">
            View Open Positions
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* Hero Section */
  .hero-section {
    padding: 160px 0 100px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a101c 0%, #0f172a 100%);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: 
      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 50%, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 50%, rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.15) 0%, transparent 50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 32px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-content {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
    border-radius: 9999px;
    color: #06b6d4;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin: 0 0 24px 0;
    color: white;
  }

  .title-gradient {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #06b6d4 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #94a3b8;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  /* Mission Section */
  .mission-section {
    padding: 120px 0;
    background: #0f172a;
  }

  .mission-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .mission-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: white;
    margin: 0 0 24px 0;
  }

  .text-large {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #d1d5db;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .text-muted {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: #94a3b8;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .stats-card {
    background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.6);
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 48px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  }

  .stat-item {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-value {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #06b6d4 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .stat-label {
    color: #94a3b8;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .stat-divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
    margin: 32px 0;
  }

  /* Story Section */
  .story-section {
    padding: 120px 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a101c 0%, #0f172a 100%);
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #64748b;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .timeline {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .timeline-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .timeline-item:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .timeline-item:last-child .timeline-marker::after {
    display: none;
  }

  .timeline-marker {
    position: relative;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .timeline-marker::before {
    content: '';
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #06b6d4 100%);
    display: block;
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5);
  }

  .timeline-marker::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 9px;
    top: 20px;
    bottom: -48px;
    width: 2px;
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
  }

  .timeline-content {
    flex: 1;
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  .timeline-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
    margin: 0 0 12px 0;
  }

  .timeline-text {
    color: #94a3b8;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Values Section */
  .values-section {
    padding: 120px 0;
    background: #0f172a;
  }

  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .values-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .value-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8) 0%, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.4) 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 40px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .value-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
  }

  .value-icon {
    width: 72px;
    height: 72px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2) 0%, rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.1) 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
    border-radius: 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: #06b6d4;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .value-card:hover .value-icon {
    transform: scale(1.1) rotate(5deg);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
  }

  .value-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
  }

  .value-text {
    color: #94a3b8;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Backed Section */
  .backed-section {
    padding: 120px 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a101c 0%, #0f172a 100%);
  }

  .backed-content {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8) 0%, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.4) 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
    border-radius: 32px;
    padding: 64px;
    display: grid;
    gap: 64px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .backed-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }

  .backed-stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .backed-stat-card {
    background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.6);
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 32px 24px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .backed-stat-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .backed-stat-value {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #06b6d4 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .backed-stat-label {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #94a3b8;
  }

  /* CTA Section */
  .cta-section {
    padding: 120px 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1) 0%, rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.05) 100%);
  }

  .cta-content {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cta-title {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: white;
    margin: 0 0 24px 0;
  }

  .cta-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #94a3b8;
    margin: 0 0 48px 0;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 16px 32px;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .btn-lg {
    padding: 18px 36px;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #06b6d4 100%);
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
    color: #06b6d4;
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
    border-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5);
  }

  /* AI Text Animation */
  .ai-text {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6 0%, #a78bfa 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    animation: violetPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    font-weight: inherit;
  }

  @keyframes violetPulse {
    0%, 100% {
      opacity: 1;
      filter: brightness(1);
    }
    50% {
      opacity: 0.85;
      filter: brightness(1.3);
    }
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-title {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .cta-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .backed-content {
      padding: 40px 24px;
    }

    .stats-card {
      padding: 32px 24px;
    }

    .stat-divider {
      margin: 24px 0;
    }
  }
</style>